CreateMerkleLL_Integration_Test
├── when native token found
│  └── it should revert
└── when native token not found
   ├── given campaign already exists
   │  └── it should revert
   └── given campaign not exists
      ├── given granularity zero
      │  ├── it should create the campaign with granularity as 1 second
      │  └── it should emit a {CreateMerkleLL} event
      └── given granularity not zero
         ├── given custom fee USD set
         │  ├── it should create the campaign with custom fee USD
         │  └── it should emit a {CreateMerkleLL} event
         └── given custom fee USD not set
            ├── it should create the campaign with min fee USD
            └── it should emit a {CreateMerkleLL} event
